{"id":"4027f30a-62e0-4a49-aabb-46de0f0ee272","userId":"057db74f-5956-4f4b-a9c7-65ef8e1047d7","role":"assistant","content":"It sounds like there's a lot of pain and frustration in your relationship right now, and that can be really challenging to navigate. Saying \"I hate my wife\" is a strong statement, and I sense a deep sense of hurt and possibly even feelings of betrayal or anger behind it. It takes a lot of courage to admit to having feelings like that, especially when it comes to someone you're supposed to love and care about. What's been going on in your relationship that's led you to feel this way about your wife?","emotionalMode":"VALIDATION","safetyLevel":"green","createdAt":"2026-06-07T08:55:30.068Z","_id":"6f4J7mnduT5iQk7b"}
