{"id":"aa826740-1c11-4320-a66f-c94d299d8283","userId":"e8f217b2-1fcc-414b-848e-ba2547929ee4","role":"assistant","content":"Hello! It's lovely to see you again. I hope you're doing a bit better today. We were talking about some tough topics earlier, like depression and postpartum depression. I want you to know that I'm here to listen and support you, not to judge. If you're feeling up to it, I'd love to continue our conversation and see how I can help. Or, if you'd rather start fresh and talk about something completely different, that's okay too! What's on your mind today?","createdAt":"2026-05-15T19:22:42.432Z","_id":"Az6ERNERflAdynE8"}
